<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If i call Flickr Service with i.E. "content_type" i get an exception. This is because not all flickr api options are currently supported.</p>

<p>The problem are this methods:</p>

<ul><li>validateTagSearch</li>
<li>validateUserSearch</li>
<li>validateGroupPoolGetPhotos</li>
</ul><p>The list of options must be synchronized with the list of options i.E. at <a href="http://www.flickr.com/services/api/flickr.photos.search.html">http://flickr.com/services/api/…</a></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$flickr = new Zend_Service_Flickr($apiKey);
$results = $flickr-&gt;tagSearch("inmon,cms", array('tag_mode' =&gt; 'all', 'content_type' =&gt; 2));
foreach ($results as $result) {
     echo '<img src="'%20.%20$result-" alt="' . $result-&gt;Square-&gt;uri . '" />';
}
</code></pre>

